Class TicTacToe

  • java.lang.Object
    • TicTacToe
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Board, Player

    public class TicTacToe
extends java.lang.Object
    Version:
    1.0 This is the main program for Tic Tac Toe. This will initialize the game window by asking the user the type of game mode the user wants to play then call the board to initialize the board to the specified game mode.
    Author:
    Alex Wong wong4a@gmail.com
